data.description: Welcome to 2173 Newville Road located on the outskirts of Carlisle Pa. This well maintained Four bed two bath rancher situated on .47 of an acre is looking for its new owner. Walking through the front door you will be greeted with a beautiful breeze way that has new ceramic plank  flooring. Venturing forward will lead you into the nicely sized living room that is accompanied with a wood/coal stove and ample amount of natural light. The living room has an exterior exit door to the back deck and one of the four bedrooms is located off of the living room. Let's take a stroll back through the breeze way to view the kitchen. Admiring the kitchen you will love the window above the sink, butcher block counter tops, farm sink, and an attached dining area. Passing through the dining area our next rooms will be the second and third bedroom and the first full bath that includes a bath tub! The last room down the hall is the primary bedroom that has an attached full bath. The primary bedroom features double closets, bamboo flooring, and ample amount of natural light. Some features about the house are full unfinished basement, laundry area in the basement, Water filtration system and UV-light(installed last year), radon system, cold storage area, one car attached garage, attached carport with extra storage, and a brand new roof!
